    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/eb5cd1f206e7cd78e14e03ed37fd95e8.avif?t=1769868278\" width=800 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/d9835dfb2795fcca2c80d795e0984c0c.poster.avif?t=1769868278\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/d9835dfb2795fcca2c80d795e0984c0c.webm?t=1769868278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/d9835dfb2795fcca2c80d795e0984c0c.mp4?t=1769868278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“面容诅咒”降临世间，一旦露出面容，便会即刻丧命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类几近灭绝。在长达264年的“孤寂纪元”之后，一个象征着安全的存在出现了——面具。尽管诅咒的起源依旧笼罩在谜团之中，许多旅人仍踏上旅途，试图揭开其真相。你会努力将这诅咒从世界上解除，还是会将其力量据为己有？<br><br>选择权在你手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/67b63231e7b2e9cbd9ce789d46b07f69.avif?t=1769868278\" width=800 height=93 /></span><strong><i> </i></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/ed2328a5ac0239a1b3e1fea657fdf6b6.poster.avif?t=1769868278\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/ed2328a5ac0239a1b3e1fea657fdf6b6.webm?t=1769868278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/ed2328a5ac0239a1b3e1fea657fdf6b6.mp4?t=1769868278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/b0ef67c6c87433abae81e4a78c9536b4.avif?t=1769868278\" width=800 height=93 /></span><strong><i> </i></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/cba8b8f221363ca82fe9c0d3a5847b7d.poster.avif?t=1769868278\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/cba8b8f221363ca82fe9c0d3a5847b7d.webm?t=1769868278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/cba8b8f221363ca82fe9c0d3a5847b7d.mp4?t=1769868278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/fe1d1c54020dfcaf368426f25806c00f.avif?t=1769868278\" width=800 height=93 /></span><strong><i> </i></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/a96c092363a460952580ef8f64365fd3.poster.avif?t=1769868278\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/a96c092363a460952580ef8f64365fd3.webm?t=1769868278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110460/extras/a96c092363a460952580ef8f64365fd3.mp4?t=17